description.en: Grind Token is built on the ethereum network with one singular purpose: to serve the hustlers, grinders, and entrepreneurs in modern society. Through their network of driven entrepreneurs they have created an incredible community who supports each other’s businesses. The sole focus of Grind Token is their 1.5% start up fund that is donated to qualified applicants, to help jump start their dream businesses. Grind Token is the Shark Tank of Crypto.
